item.title: About
item.description: I am high-school student in Novi Sad, Serbia and open source enthusiast. I contributed to many large projects like Genoo, Pentoo, Lutris and imdbpy… Also I like to solve CTFs. My biggest reverse-engineering achievement is viber. My favourite language is Python. I use Gentoo Linux btw :)
